<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">国风·周南·兔罝</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson205ceb963514">
肃肃兔罝，椓之丁丁。赳赳武夫，公侯干城。<br />肃肃兔罝，施于中逵。赳赳武夫，公侯好仇。<br />肃肃兔罝，施于中林。赳赳武夫，公侯腹心。
</div>
</div>
